  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT has only been available since November 2022 providing only a short period time in which academic literature could be published regarding faculty perceptions of the use of ChatGPT.",
    "However, a review of the research reveals a few early articles that are relevant to this study.",
    "Taecharungroj (2023) collected and analyzed tweets about ChatGPT in English from November 30 to December 31, 2022, with the purpose of identifying the perceptions of early general users of ChatGPT.",
    "The Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA) topic modeling algorithm was used to answer the question \"What can ChatGPT do?\"",
    "The results revealed topics that were grouped into three domains: general topics, functional domains, and potential impacts."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Taecharungroj (2023) collected and analyzed tweets about ChatGPT in English from November 30 to December 31, 2022, with the purpose of identifying the perceptions of early general users of ChatGPT."
